# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6c.rpy:48
translate chinese u19a2s6c_9891ce96:

    # "I hear a noise in the woods, like a twig snapping, and it puts me on alert."
    "我听见林中传来声响，像是树枝断裂，这让我顿时警觉起来。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6c.rpy:50
translate chinese u19a2s6c_825f91ff:

    # gg "I don't think we're alone out here."
    gg "我觉得这里不止我们两个人。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6c.rpy:52
translate chinese u19a2s6c_ee510045:

    # sg "What was that? I heard a noise."
    sg "那是什么？我听见动静了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6c.rpy:54
translate chinese u19a2s6c_8629b5b4:

    # bn "I don't think we're alone here."
    bn "我觉得这里不止我们两个人。"

