translate chinese u19a2s6c_33ed9226:

    # gg "Are those guns magic? I sense something from them."
    gg "那些枪是魔法武器吗？我感觉它们有某种气息。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6c.rpy:207
translate chinese u19a2s6c_d211965d:

    # det "Yeah they are. They're very special to me."
    det "是的。它们对我来说非常特别。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6c.rpy:209
translate chinese u19a2s6c_0f3c13f7:

    # sg "Nice to meet you! I'm Kendra."
    sg "很高兴认识你！我是肯德拉。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6c.rpy:210
translate chinese u19a2s6c_3ec570f2:

    # sg "That was incredible, the way you were like \"BLAM! POW! KABLOOEY!\""
    sg "刚才太厉害了，你那“砰！啪！轰！”的样子。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6c.rpy:211
translate chinese u19a2s6c_51ce01e8:

    # det "Hah, yeah. Thanks."
    det "哈哈，是啊。谢谢。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6c.rpy:212
translate chinese u19a2s6c_9fb22c06:

    # det "I don't love doing it, but I can't say I'm too sad to see those people unable to hurt anybody else."
    det "我并不喜欢这么做，但看到那些人再也伤害不了别人，我倒也不觉得太难过。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6c.rpy:213
translate chinese u19a2s6c_518f546b:

    # sg "Heck yeah. Fuck those guys."
    sg "当然啦。去他妈的那些家伙。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6c.rpy:215
translate chinese u19a2s6c_c628a769:

    # bn "I'm Juliana. Nice to meet you, Jez."
    bn "我是朱莉安娜。很高兴认识你，杰兹。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6c.rpy:216
translate chinese u19a2s6c_86d67a4d:

    # bn "Were those guys really that bad? They deserved what you did to them?"
    bn "那些家伙真的有那么坏吗？他们活该被你那样对待？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6c.rpy:217
translate chinese u19a2s6c_e2b6a9a7:

    # det "You heard what they said they were going to do to you."
    det "你听见他们说要对你做什么了吧。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6c.rpy:218
translate chinese u19a2s6c_8a31e387:

    # det "It's not the first time they've done this. They deserved it."
    det "这又不是他们第一次干这种事了。他们活该。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6c.rpy:219
translate chinese u19a2s6c_3e4cedd2:

    # bn "Yes... I guess so. It's just... sad."
    bn "是啊……我想也是。只是……有点悲哀。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene6c.rpy:220
translate chinese u19a2s6c_2d8dbe51:

    # det "I don't disagree."
    det "我也不否认。"

